entry.title: Publication of MLJC Annual Report 2021
entry.content: The Machine Learning Journal Club is pleased to publish the Annual Activity Report 2021 where the most relevant scientific and outreach activity of the past year is presented. This report is a great opportunity to thank the several people and institutions that contributed to our activities with their expertise, resources and support. Take a look
